@startuml PaymentProFlow
title TIMELAPSE - Ativação Pro (UC003 - RF010)
actor User
participant DesktopApp
participant ControlPlane
participant AuthAPI
participant LicenseManager
participant EmailService

User -> DesktopApp: Clica em "Ativar Pro"
DesktopApp -> User: Solicita código da organização
User -> DesktopApp: Informa código
DesktopApp -> User: Solicita email
User -> DesktopApp: Informa email

DesktopApp -> ControlPlane: POST /auth/magic-link {email, orgCode}
ControlPlane -> AuthAPI: Validar orgCode + registrar Magic Link
AuthAPI -> EmailService: Enviar Magic Link
EmailService -> User: Recebe email

User -> DesktopApp: Clica no Link (ou insere token)
DesktopApp -> ControlPlane: POST /auth/verify {token}
ControlPlane -> AuthAPI: Validar token
AuthAPI -> ControlPlane: JWT + User + Org

ControlPlane -> LicenseManager: Ativar licença Pro para org
LicenseManager -> ControlPlane: Licença ativada
ControlPlane -> DesktopApp: Sucesso - Pro ativo
DesktopApp -> User: Acesso Pro liberado
@enduml
